(196, 'taxonomy_term_11', 'a:11:{s:7:\"popular\";s:3:\"yes\";s:9:\"store_url\";s:27:\"https://www.dominos.com.au/\";s:10:\"store_logo\";s:75:\"https://demo.clipmydeals.com/4/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dominos_logo.jpeg\";s:11:\"store_intro\";s:1730:\"<h2>WELCOME TO DOMINO\\\'S PIZZA – WHERE EVERY SLICE TELLS A STORY OF CHEESY GOODNESS!</h2>\r\n<p>At Domino\\\'s, we\\\'re not just about delivering pizzas; we\\\'re about delivering happiness, one piping-hot pie at a time. Our secret recipe dough, savory sauces, and premium toppings come together to create a flavor explosion that\\\'ll have your taste buds doing a happy dance.</p>\r\n<p>With a legacy dating back decades, Domino\\\'s has perfected the art of pizza-making. Whether you\\\'re a fan of classic pepperoni, crave the veggie-packed delight of our Garden-Fresh pizza, or want to spice things up with our fiery Buffalo Chicken, we\\\'ve got something to satisfy every craving.</p>\r\n<p>But it\\\'s not just about the pizza – our sides and desserts are equally drool-worthy. From crispy chicken wings to mouthwatering lava cakes, we\\\'ve got all the fixings to make your meal complete.</p>\r\n<p>Ordering from Domino\\\'s is a breeze, thanks to our user-friendly online platform and lightning-fast delivery service. With just a few clicks, you can have a hot and delicious pizza delivered straight to your door, ready to be devoured.</p>\r\n<p>So why wait? Treat yourself to a slice of happiness today with Domino\\\'s Pizza. Don\\\'t forget to check out our latest deals and discounts on your favorite pies – because saving money never tasted so good!</p>\r\n<p>Hot Deals Alert! Save big on your next Domino\\\'s order with exclusive coupons and promotions available only on our coupon website. Whether you\\\'re craving a classic Margherita or want to try something new, we\\\'ve got discounts that\\\'ll make your wallet and your taste buds happy. Don\\\'t miss out – grab your coupon now and indulge in the ultimate pizza experienc