(47, 47, 'stores', 'Under Armour is a leading athletic performance brand renowned for its innovative sportswear, footwear, and accessories. Founded in 1996, the company revolutionized athletic apparel with its moisture-wicking fabric technology, designed to keep athletes cool, dry, and light during intense workouts. Under Armour caters to athletes and fitness enthusiasts across all levels, offering high-performance gear that combines cutting-edge design with functionality. Its extensive product range includes training apparel, running shoes, compression wear, and sports accessories, all crafted to enhance performance and comfort. With a commitment to empowering individuals through sports, Under Armour continues to set the standard for athletic innovation and excellence.', 0, 0),
