(43, 43, 'stores', 'BasharaCare is a premium online platform specializing in skincare, beauty, and wellness products in the Middle East. With a focus on providing high-quality, dermatologist-recommended brands, BasharaCare caters to a wide range of skin concerns and beauty needs. The platform offers an extensive selection of skincare, haircare, body care, and cosmetic products from globally renowned and trusted brands. Known for its personalized shopping experience, BasharaCare provides detailed product information, expert advice, and tailored recommendations to help customers achieve their beauty goals. With convenient delivery options and exceptional customer service, BasharaCare has become a trusted destination for beauty enthusiasts in the region.', 0, 0),
(33, 33, 'brands', 'OnePlus creates premium, user-centric technology that challenges market conventions and the industry status quo. Founded in 2013 around the bold Never Settle mantra, OnePlus consistently creates premium devices and software that provide the best user experience possible.', 0, 3),
(34, 34, 'brands', 'American Tourister\'s commitment to precision and durability is unparalleled. Each luggage piece is a testament to craftsmanship that not only carries your belongings but ensures they arrive intact, ready for the next adventure. Now, with our exclusive deals, embark on your explorations with savings in tow.', 0, 2),
(35, 35, 'brands', 'Welcome to the world of IKEA, where innovation, affordability, and style converge to transform your living space into a haven of comfort and functionality. As a global leader in home furnishings, IKEA is renowned for its Scandinavian design philosophy, seamlessly blending form with function to create products that resonate with modern living.', 0, 1),
(36, 36, 'brands', 'Puma\'s legacy is a narrative of passion, performance, and panache. From the iconic Puma Suede to cutting-edge sportswear technology, each product is a testament to the brand\'s commitment to innovation and pushing the envelope.', 0, 1),
(37, 37, 'brands', 'Marmot transcends mere branding; it embodies a philosophy that inspires you to welcome the elements and savor the exhilaration of exploration. Embark on an adventure like never before, as our exclusive Marmot deals and offers make the irresistible allure of the wilderness even more compelling.', 0, 1),
(38, 38, 'brands', 'Motorola\'s journey is a narrative of constant innovation. From the first mobile phone call made on a Motorola device to the latest breakthroughs in smartphone technology, the brand has consistently set the pace for the industry. With a commitment to pushing boundaries, each Motorola device carries the torch of a legacy built on groundbreaking ideas.', 0, 2),
(39, 39, 'brands', 'Indulge in a world of glamour at Sephora, where beauty takes center stage, and self-expression knows no limits. Our coupon website is your gateway to exclusive Sephora deals, offering discounts on a plethora of cosmetics, skincare, and fragrances. Sephora is not just a beauty store; it\'s a sanctuary of innovation and luxury.', 0, 2),
(40, 40, 'brands', 'Indulge in the epitome of denim excellence with Levi\'s – a brand that has seamlessly woven its way into the fabric of timeless fashion. From iconic blue jeans to contemporary styles, Levi\'s is a testament to enduring style and authenticity. Now, with our exclusive Levi\'s coupons, you can embrace this legacy without compromising your budget.', 0, 2),
