(46, 46, 'stores', 'Gap is a globally recognized clothing and accessories brand known for its timeless, casual, and modern style. Founded in 1969, Gap offers a wide range of apparel for men, women, children, and babies, focusing on quality, comfort, and versatility. The brand is celebrated for its iconic denim collections, classic T-shirts, and wardrobe essentials that cater to everyday wear and diverse fashion preferences. With a commitment to sustainability and ethical practices, Gap continues to innovate in design and materials while maintaining its reputation as a go-to destination for stylish, high-quality basics.', 0, 0),
(44, 44, 'stores', 'Bloomingdale\'s is a luxury department store renowned for its premium selection of fashion, beauty, home, and lifestyle products. Originating in New York City, Bloomingdale\'s has become a global symbol of style and sophistication. In the UAE, Bloomingdale\'s operates as a flagship destination for high-end shopping, featuring an extensive range of designer apparel, accessories, cosmetics, and home décor. Known for its impeccable customer service, curated collections, and exclusive offerings, Bloomingdale\'s caters to discerning shoppers seeking the latest trends and timeless elegance. The store also offers personalized services, including styling consultations and bespoke gift options, making it a favorite among luxury retail enthusiasts.', 0, 0),
(42, 42, 'stores', 'Noon GCC is one of the leading e-commerce platforms in the Gulf Cooperation Council (GCC) region, offering a wide range of products including electronics, fashion, beauty, home goods, and groceries. With a strong presence in countries like the UAE, Saudi Arabia, and Egypt, Noon provides a user-friendly shopping experience, fast delivery options, and attractive deals. It has become a go-to destination for online shoppers in the region, combining global brands with local products to cater to diverse customer preferences.', 0, 1),
(48, 48, 'stores', 'Waya is a premium brand specializing in high-quality hair care products designed to nourish, protect, and enhance all hair types. Offering a range of shampoos, conditioners, treatments, and styling products, Waya uses natural ingredients combined with cutting-edge formulations to provide effective solutions for healthier, more vibrant hair. The brand focuses on sustainability, cruelty-free practices, and products that promote the well-being of both hair and scalp. Whether you are looking to restore moisture, add volume, or protect from damage, Waya offers luxurious and eco-conscious products that cater to every hair care need.', 0, 0),
(49, 49, 'stores', 'Beluar offers premium air fresheners designed to enhance the atmosphere of any space with refreshing and long-lasting scents. Whether you\'re looking to neutralize odors or simply create a more pleasant environment, Beluar’s range of air fresheners provides a variety of fragrances to suit every preference. Using high-quality ingredients, Beluar ensures that each product delivers a clean, fresh scent without being overpowering. With innovative and user-friendly designs, Beluar air fresheners are perfect for homes, offices, and cars, providing an instant uplift to your surroundings.', 0, 0),
(50, 50, 'stores', 'Danube Home is a leading furniture and home decor brand in Saudi Arabia, offering an extensive range of stylish, functional, and high-quality furniture for every room in the house. Whether you\'re looking to furnish your living room, bedroom, kitchen, or office, Danube Home provides a wide selection of products to meet all your home decor needs. Known for its elegant designs, durable materials, and attention to detail, Danube Home offers furniture that combines comfort and aesthetic appeal. The brand is committed to offering affordable solutions that transform any space into a beautiful and comfortable home.', 0, 0),
(51, 51, 'stores', 'Level Shoes is a globally recognized destination for luxury footwear and accessories, offering an unparalleled collection of designer brands, emerging labels, and exclusive collaborations. With its flagship stores in the GCC, Level Shoes provides a curated shopping experience that caters to diverse tastes and styles. From elegant heels and statement sneakers to timeless loafers and versatile boots, the brand showcases a wide range of options for men, women, and children. Level Shoes is synonymous with quality, craftsmanship, and innovation, making it the ultimate destination for footwear enthusiasts and fashion lovers.', 0, 0),
(52, 52, 'stores', 'The Body Shop offers eco-friendly, cruelty-free skincare, body care, and beauty products made with natural, ethically sourced ingredients. Discover feel-good, sustainable beauty that loves your skin and the planet!', 0, 0),
